name: 2 | Halloween is here
description:
Anecdote of 2019 when a unknown girl asked Chulito for a photo and he, without thinking, included me in it.

There is nothing better than "being with someone who loves you in public, in private and behind your back". 

Don't settle for being next to someone who doesn't give you the place you deserve in their life, if with love you have shown that you do deserve it.
